    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in breathtaking showroom condition, this vehicle is a true time capsule for the discerning collector. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from stone chips, swirls, or blemishes, having been exclusively hand-washed and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, and the interior retains that distinct new-car aroma, with every surface free of sun fading or scratches. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with the tactile precision of the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a meticulous and comprehensive file of preventative maintenance records performed solely by certified specialists. This is not merely a well-kept used car; it is a flawless example of automotive preservation, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For those seeking the absolute best example on the market, this is it.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
