      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece maintained to the highest standards of excellence. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, offering a pristine aesthetic paired with flawless mechanical integrity. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from a new showroom acquisition. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a testament to superior care and engineering.",
