      "description": "This E46 M3 is a peerless example of Bavarian engineering, centered around the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS timing. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via an M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a documented subframe reinforcement and zero evidence of fatigue. Finished in factory Carbon Black metallic with a pristine Nappa leather interior, this specimen delivers a linear power band and telepathic steering feedback. It has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service history, ensuring peak performance and mechanical longevity.",
